   "source": [
    "#  Clustering\n",
    "\n",
    "In this notebook we are going to consider cost-based clustering, in particular k-means, and hierarchical clustering, and run and compare them on some simple datasets.\n",
    "\n",
    "## K-means\n",
    "\n",
    "We are going to use some synthetic datasets to understand various aspects of Lloyd's algorithm for the k-means  clustering problem."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
